- **Badge** not "Pass" for Пропуск (US FM standard: Brivo, GSA, ServiceNow Guardian, MRI, AlertEnterprise). "Pass" alone has zero US FM usage.
- **Clicked** (not "Selected") for button interactions in trigger text. You click buttons; you select from dropdowns.
- **Normal** / **Not normal** for Норм / Не норм (spelled out, not abbreviations norm/notnorm)
