# Comindware Localization Skill — v2 (Agentic SDL Trados)

Complete AI-driven localization pipeline for Comindware Platform. Two-phase: alias-based (Volga_verified_complete.json) and non-alias (extracted_keys.jsonl).

## Pipeline Overview

```
┌──────────────────┐     ┌────────────────────┐     ┌───────────────────┐     ┌──────────┐
│ extract_keys.py  │────▶│prepare_extracted.py│────▶│batch_non_alias.py │────▶│ git     │
│ (recursive JSON  │     │ (auto-fill Latin,  │     │ (100-row tables,  │     │ commit  │
│  key extraction) │     │  TM pre-fills,     │     │  user approval,   │     │ per     │
│                  │     │  approved-tracking)│     │  TM upsert)       │     │ ~200    │
└──────────────────┘     └────────────────────┘     └───────────────────┘     └──────────┘
```

## Quick Start

```bash
# Phase 0: Extract all keys from JSON config
python scripts/extract_keys.py                    # → localization/extracted_keys.jsonl

# Phase 0: Prepare (auto-fill Latin, pre-fill TM, build queue)
